1.   FILE_ATTRIBUTE_RECALL_ON_OPEN, FILE_ATTRIBUTE_RECALL_ON_DATA_ACCESS, FILE_ATTRIBUTE_STRICTLY_SEQUENTIAL.   .

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
drkns 2019-08-16 23:06:24+01:00 - build 5451

1. Crash when importing malformed xml.

