   The code page affects only the text part.
   Before: "0000000048: 006C 0061 007A 0079  0020 0064 006F 0067  lazy dog"
   After:  "0000000048: 6C 00 61 00 7A 00 79 00  20 00 64 00 6F 00 67 00  lazy dog"

