--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
drkns 2011-12-05 17:05:29+02:00 - build 2282

1. Mantis#0001935: when importing from xml, variables are placed into constants section

1. More on Mantis#0001221.

                        

1. Mantis#0001935:    xml     

