1. "[x] File processing (OpenFilePlugin)" switch in plugin manager settings is now 3-positional:
     [ ] - don't show menu;
     [?] - show menu everywhere but cases "enter an archive with Enter" and "search in archives";
     [x] - show menu everywhere.

