     N=BM.Add()
     N=BM.Clear()
     N=BM.Next()
     N=BM.Prev()
     N=BM.Stat()
   Note that...
   a) math in "BM.Stat()" needs redesign (something like
StatStackBookmark())
   b) "BM.XXX" can be something other than "editor" :-)

